<lb n="1"/>§ Āṅkira<supplied reason="omitted">ca</supplied>varu<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>m Āṉimātam 9 kuṇṇakkuṭik<note n="25-2">Engraved in continuation of No. 33 above.</note>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>kovil cuppiramaṇiyacuvāmi kāriyattu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kku ka<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>ttarāṉa tāṉattā<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied> talattār toḻuciṅka
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vaḷanāṭṭu kaṇṭukoṇṭamāṇi<hi rend="grantha">kka</hi>ttil
<lb n="5"/>nāṭṭāṟku kalveṭṭi kkuṭuttapaṭi cuvāmikku naṭu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vakkoṭṭai Eṅkaḷ kiṟāmam viṭṭukkuṭuttapaṭi
<lb n="7" break="no"/>yiṉāle <hi rend="grantha">kṣā</hi>makālam tiruppaṇi Āṉāl kku
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṭi 1- kku Oru paṇam §
